metadata.name: NFT LA 2022 POAP #1
metadata.description: Created by the UNDRGRND, a free POAP on Ethereum for attendees of NFT LA 2022. Part of our 2022 tour, we're relasing POAPs at SXSW, NFT LA, and NFT NYC. Find our QR codes spread across these events and collect all 3 designs. Holders get perks to future events.
